Sergi Samper (Ex Bar&ccedil;a): &quot;The Pjanić-Arthur exchange surprised me because Arthur seems to be a great player. I like how he protects the ball. Pjanić is spectacular but it remains to be seen who the Bar&ccedil;a coach is and how Pjanić fits into the team.&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;Can Bar&ccedil;a win the Champions League? I think so, in the end the squad is very good and very talented. Although the latest feelings have not been good, in single match duels, with players at this level, anything can happen.&quot;

